# Khamar, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Khamar (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Tlyaratinsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Khamar is located 7&nbsp;km southeast of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Cherel is the nearest rural locality.
